headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires Encore Group
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced the acquisition of Waterloo, Ontario-based Encore Insurance Services Inc., dba Encore Group. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.
